  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106230/extras/b7d501fedf9c40e3f0494d3c2a67a7fc.webp?t=1740146445\" width=650 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106230/extras/3c128f628a3b09fad798411fe30c1c80.avif?t=1740146445\" width=616 height=198 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The king has passed away. The crown now entrusted in the hands of his youngest yet reckless daughter, Emmeline, has plunged all of Vex Clock into turmoil. Betrayal, false accusations and despair has driven our five plucky protagonists into taking matters into their own hands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, jump and blast your way through 20+ oil soaked levels in this action packed thirdperson/FPS hybrid, where your quest for vengeance knows no bounds, but the friends you bond with will shape the final outcome. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106230/extras/51b44feeb92fa96334262d8a2daba97f.poster.avif?t=1740146445\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106230/extras/51b44feeb92fa96334262d8a2daba97f.webm?t=1740146445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106230/extras/51b44feeb92fa96334262d8a2daba97f.mp4?t=1740146445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each character has their own weapon of choice, whether it be Lilian's long range pistol, Rosa's close quarters shotgun or Chloe's crowd control railgun. Managing your party and swapping characters during battle is the key to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106230/extras/e742e3f2245c4353511b817bebe4a682.poster.avif?t=1740146445\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106230/extras/e742e3f2245c4353511b817bebe4a682.webm?t=1740146445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106230/extras/e742e3f2245c4353511b817bebe4a682.mp4?t=1740146445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your ventures, you'll encounter personal missions. These missions will challenge you by limiting your party count, but completing them will tailor the ending you get. Will you focus on one character's story or try to help as many of them as you can? Who you choose to help in combination with another can make or break their futures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The fate of Vex Clock rests in your hands...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106230/extras/80ba51b7b6ded864a12f841c42a18dce.webp?t=1740146445\" width=650 height=40 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106230/extras/b7d501fedf9c40e3f0494d3c2a67a7fc.webp?t=1740146445\" width=650 height=40 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106230/extras/3c128f628a3b09fad798411fe30c1c80.avif?t=1740146445\" width=616 height=198 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The king has passed away. The crown now entrusted in the hands of his youngest yet reckless daughter, Emmeline, has plunged all of Vex Clock into turmoil. Betrayal, false accusations and despair has driven our five plucky protagonists into taking matters into their own hands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, jump and blast your way through 20+ oil soaked levels in this action packed thirdperson/FPS hybrid, where your quest for vengeance knows no bounds, but the friends you bond with will shape the final outcome. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106230/extras/51b44feeb92fa96334262d8a2daba97f.poster.avif?t=1740146445\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106230/extras/51b44feeb92fa96334262d8a2daba97f.webm?t=1740146445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106230/extras/51b44feeb92fa96334262d8a2daba97f.mp4?t=1740146445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each character has their own weapon of choice, whether it be Lilian's long range pistol, Rosa's close quarters shotgun or Chloe's crowd control railgun. Managing your party and swapping characters during battle is the key to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106230/extras/e742e3f2245c4353511b817bebe4a682.poster.avif?t=1740146445\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106230/extras/e742e3f2245c4353511b817bebe4a682.webm?t=1740146445\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106230/extras/e742e3f2245c4353511b817bebe4a682.mp4?t=1740146445\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your ventures, you'll encounter personal missions. These missions will challenge you by limiting your party count, but completing them will tailor the ending you get. Will you focus on one character's story or try to help as many of them as you can? Who you choose to help in combination with another can make or break their futures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The fate of Vex Clock rests in your hands...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2106230/extras/80ba51b7b6ded864a12f841c42a18dce.webp?t=1740146445\" width=650 height=40 /></span></p>",
